&GATEWAY
  Title = TBHP S0 geometry optimization with SA4-CASSCF(6e,4o)
  Coord = tbhp_unopt.xyz
  Basis = cc-pVDZ
  Group = NoSymm

>>> DoWhile

&SEWARD

&RASSCF
  Title = TBHP SA4-CASSCF(6e,4o), optimize S0
